::Aerotaur::
       He looks up from where he was watching the Predacons leave.  "Yes, 
Windlord, I am fine."  He turns and walks over to him.  "Although it appears 
you are not."  He shrugs and gestures to the Predacons.  "But at least we 
have won the day."
